{"tid":1387222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家我地喺道德嘅最高地，點解仲要繼續勇武？","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:09:33.000Z","uid":16086,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"43c8db7d4e30dffae63d000d3c9cf7206ee01dab","tid":1387222,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為前線勇武對和理非冇信心！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家睇曬，覺得我講唔啱再屌我。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔可以代表所有勇武手足，但我係咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n好坦白，現時嘅情況，我地勇武手足點會唔清楚，但係勇武繼續承受犧牲嘅風險，都要企喺最前同班狗對抗，其中一個原因係驚萬一勇武真係退落黎，而和理非承接唔到運動嘅下一步，我地個抗爭就會全面收皮。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望所有人，都用你地嘅行動回應勇武手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日，全港大罷工。</span></span><br />\n和理非唔需要再你地個口同鍵盤去勸勇武，你地用行動就得，你係真心擔心前線，唔想佢地犧牲，唔該你同我罷工，如果唔係你咪再嘥口水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有咁樣，和理非先係真正咁支持勇武手足。</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b91fa12e49dfdff8e27154559e048bfb4f20cbd","tid":1387222,"uid":16086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日，全港大罷工。</span></span>"},{"pid":"21d8107bb238a1d58cb3414ff6edfd79fac2e2fc","tid":1387222,"uid":16086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日，全港大罷工。</span></span>"},{"pid":"cfa640cd8cd018ee8b60e6cd42e737fb1d4e161e","tid":1387222,"uid":16086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5日，全港大罷工。</span></span>"},{"pid":"3663042f3e1b3ffd12015674a454af2bbe51cfd9","tid":1387222,"uid":16086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5日，全港大罷工。</span></span